    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 26 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 14 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 30</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You rain spear-shaped bolts of lightning down on the battlefield, targeting 2d6 creatures and/or structures within the area. Each target is hit by 1d4+1 spears, each dealing 1d8+1 electricity damage. The technique can affect each target only once, and structures take double damage. In a crowded area with many structures (like a town), targets are chosen at random.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the number of targets by 1d6, up to 5d6 total.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
